      Hello! I'm Syaiful, a software engineer based in Indonesia. I specialize
      in building web applications and have professional experience working with
      JavaScript, TypeScript, and React. I'm passionate about learning new
      technologies and sharing my knowledge with others. In my free time, I
      enjoy reading books, playing video games, and watching movies. Feel free
      to contact me if you have any questions or just want to say hi!
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Info -->
